## Barcode Strips


::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="6,7|6,7,8|6,7,8,9|6,7,8,9,10|3,|10"}
g +
  geom_boxplot(
     position = position_nudge(x = .15),
     width = .35
  ) +
  geom_point(
    shape = "-",
    size = 8,
    alpha = .1,
    position = position_nudge(x = -.15)
  )
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
